reviews.text: The food size is over-abundant and beyond my appetite although I like the taste very much.  It's not industrial food like other shops but looks very genuine made inside the shop.  Will definitely check back again.
Very nice!
Good. Very good. I am not a Viet cuisine expert but dined there twice in as many days.  Beef pho and summer rolls. Wow.

Not great. I guess if you just wanna fill your stomach, this is a ok place to go. Price is above average. Feel like the soup used a lot of msg. Very thirty after the meal. Meal is small . Pork chops was fine.

It's funny that when the paper on the table listed out what are needed for a traditional pho but not all the ingredients listed are served by the restaurant. Or maybe they did, just not to the standard I found in Vietnam. The  spices in pho are very important to me but there aren't enough served as in Vietnam. The beef is great the soup is great too. It's not traditional enough but it's a good bargain.

reviews.text: 夏天空調不夠涼，牛坑腩太多筋，其他的還可以。
蕃茄牛腩粉絲味道很好，下午茶份量仍很足，湯底真材實料，會常去
食物味道好 但贵咗些 環境幾舒服
食物和環境都還可以,價錢以日間相宜,晚市六点後會比日間貴三份一左右
😀😀 啲價錢適中呢啲嘢就幾好食都覺得好去
